sub_title: Global Account Director Trade and Global Meetings & Events | Air France-KLM-Delta
summary: As a strategic and hands-on experienced international manager in the field of Marketing & Sales B2T, B2B and B2C, I have worked with some of the world's leading companies, developing and implementing strategies that have resulted in increased market share, revenue growth, and improved customer satisfaction. Currently, I am in charge of optimizing the global commercial partnership between Air France-KLM-Delta and BCD Travel and next to that the Air France-KLM global meetings & events program.
